# =============================================================================
# AGING SIGNS TO PREVENT (Performance Degradation)
# =============================================================================
PREVENTS:
  - Fine Lines (minor slowdowns) → Query optimization
  - Wrinkles (major slowdowns) → Architectural refactoring
  - Age Spots (hotspots) → Profiling and optimization
  - Sagging (memory leaks) → Garbage collection tuning
  - Dullness (poor cache hits) → Caching strategy
  - Texture Issues (inconsistent performance) → Load balancing
  - Volume Loss (capacity exhaustion) → Proactive scaling
  - Elasticity Loss (slow adaptation) → Continuous optimization

# =============================================================================
# WARNINGS & PRECAUTIONS
# =============================================================================
WARNINGS:
  - May cause "purging" in first week (temporary regression during optimization)
  - Start with lower concentration (gentle optimization first)
  - Increase gradually (build up optimization intensity)
  - Always use sunscreen (maintain security during optimization)
  - Can cause sensitivity (false positive regressions)
  - Discontinue if severe irritation (> 10% performance loss)
  - Consult professional for prescription strength (major refactoring)

PRECAUTIONS:
  - Patch test first (pilot optimization on subset)
  - Use at night initially (off-peak optimization)
  - Combine with moisturizer (context preservation)
  - Avoid over-use (excessive optimization has diminishing returns)
  - Monitor for reactions (watch metrics closely)
  - Adjust based on skin type (customize for architecture)

RETINOL_PRECAUTIONS (Code Optimization Warnings):
  - Start slow: Begin with 0.1% strength (minor refactoring)
  - Build tolerance: Increase to 1.0% over months (major refactoring)
  - Expect purging: Temporary slowdown during refactoring
  - Sun sensitivity: More vulnerable during optimization
  - Not for sensitive systems: Skip for real-time critical systems
  - Pregnancy concerns: Avoid during major migrations

# =============================================================================
# CONTRAINDICATIONS
# =============================================================================
CONTRAINDICATIONS:
  - Active system failures (repair first with scar-repair.skn)
  - Extremely sensitive systems (real-time medical devices)
  - Systems under heavy load (optimize during off-peak)
  - Recent major changes (wait 2 weeks for stability)
  - Insufficient monitoring (blind optimization is dangerous)
  - Known allergies to profiling (overhead-sensitive systems)

